nodes.text: Star Wars Galaxy Magazine 5 is the fifth issue of Star Wars Galaxy Magazine. It was published by Topps in October 1995. The Deluxe Collectors' Edition of issue 5, exclusive to subscribers and comic stores, came polybagged with promotional trading cards for 1996 Topps Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Widevision, 1995 Topps Star Wars Master Visions, and 1995 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 3. This issue also included a Ralph McQuarrie fold-out poster.
